969
00:35:45,179 --> 00:35:50,639
[SPEAKER_02] Kad kažemo komunikacija, komunikacija je većini ljudi nešto što se podrazumijeva.

970
00:35:50,639 --> 00:35:54,179
[SPEAKER_02] I mi komuniciramo užasno automatski.

971
00:35:55,619 --> 00:36:02,159
[SPEAKER_02] I problem tu nastaje, kada mi uzimamo komunikaciju zdravo za gotovo i ne trudimo se oko nje.

972
00:36:02,159 --> 00:36:09,659
[SPEAKER_02] Istraživanja pokazuje da najveći postotak razvoda brakova dolazi zbog loše komunikacije.

973
00:36:09,659 --> 00:36:16,539
[SPEAKER_02] Najveći broj otkaza na poslu dolazi zbog loše komunikacije s nadređenima ili s kolegama.

974
00:36:16,539 --> 00:36:21,300
[SPEAKER_02] E sad, kada istražujemo gdje ljudi griješe u toj komunikaciji,

975
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:28,800
[SPEAKER_02] a onda dolazimo do jedne zanimljive činjenice, a to je da mi nismo fokusirani u komunikaciji,

976
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:35,119
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno da mi komuniciramo s drugima onako kako bi mi htjeli da se komunicira s nama.

977
00:36:35,119 --> 00:36:37,739
[SPEAKER_02] A svatko od nas je potpuno drugačije.

978
00:36:37,739 --> 00:36:41,500
[SPEAKER_02] Neko je direktan, neko voli da mu kažete sve u lice,

979
00:36:41,500 --> 00:36:46,860
[SPEAKER_02] neko je introvertiran pa će pripaziti malo kako će,

980
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:48,659
[SPEAKER_02] neko će diplomatski govoriti.

981
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:54,179
[SPEAKER_02] I ako mi sada svojim načinom komunikacije razgovaramo sa svima,

982
00:36:54,179 --> 00:36:56,019
[SPEAKER_02] naravno da ćemo uočiti nesporazume.

983
00:36:56,019 --> 00:37:00,119
[SPEAKER_02] I zato kažu da je to dijamantno pravilo komuniciranja,

984
00:37:00,119 --> 00:37:07,780
[SPEAKER_02] da mi s drugima trebamo komunicirati onako kako oni očekuju da se komunicira s njima.

985
00:37:07,780 --> 00:37:11,840
[SPEAKER_02] A to znači malo empatije, to znači malo sosjećanja,

986
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,679
[SPEAKER_02] to znači ući malo u njegov svijet.

987
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:17,739
[SPEAKER_02] Ali mi to nećemo napraviti ako nam nije stalo do čovjeka.

988
00:37:17,739 --> 00:37:21,320
[SPEAKER_02] Ako nam nije stalo do čovjeka, onda ćemo mi komunicirati rutinski.

989
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:26,119
[SPEAKER_02] Ako nam je stalo do čovjeka, mi ćemo se potruditi prilagoditi svoju komunikaciju.

990
00:37:26,119 --> 00:37:28,119
[SPEAKER_02] I sada tu dolazimo do one ljubavi.

991
00:37:28,119 --> 00:37:32,199
[SPEAKER_02] Ako ne osjećamo ljubav prema čovjeku, koji je preko puta nas,

992
00:37:32,199 --> 00:37:34,260
[SPEAKER_02] onda će komunikacija biti loša.

993
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:37,440
[SPEAKER_02] Ako ga volimo, ako nam je stalo do njega, ako ga poštujemo,

994
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:39,739
[SPEAKER_02] onda ćemo se mi truditi prilagoditi tu komunikaciju.

995
00:37:39,739 --> 00:37:45,400
[SPEAKER_02] I ima jedan američki veliki guru u komunikaciji,

996
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:48,119
[SPEAKER_02] koji je ateist, uspud budi rečeno,

997
00:37:48,119 --> 00:37:52,780
[SPEAKER_02] koji kaže, neka vam ljudi postanu važni koje se usrećete.

998
00:37:52,780 --> 00:37:57,039
[SPEAKER_02] Kada vam ljudi postanu važni, onda ćete vi počniti mijenjati komunikaciju.

999
00:37:58,039 --> 00:38:00,360
[SPEAKER_02] Drugo pravilo koje on kaže,

1000
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:04,179
[SPEAKER_02] Bog ne me stvorio jedna usta i dva uha.

1001
00:38:04,179 --> 00:38:09,219
[SPEAKER_02] Što znači da bi duplo više trebali slušati druge nego im docirati.

1002
00:38:09,219 --> 00:38:16,800
[SPEAKER_02] Znači otvoriti uši i srce za potrebe, za težnje, za očekivanja

1003
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:22,699
[SPEAKER_02] i postavljati više pitanja da dođemo mi do čovjeka koji je preko puta nas.

1004
00:38:22,699 --> 00:38:27,800
[SPEAKER_02] A onda ćemo mi moći docirati, onda ćemo moći dati pravi odgovor i druge.

1005
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:34,280
[SPEAKER_02] Treće pravilo je da budemo verodostojni, autentični.

1006
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:38,340
[SPEAKER_02] Ne mi dociramo drugima, a mi to ne živimo.

1007
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:41,699
[SPEAKER_02] To ljudi jako brzo skuže, mi onda smo neverodostojni.

1008
00:38:41,699 --> 00:38:45,300
[SPEAKER_02] Ako oni shvate da mi stojimo iza svojih riječi,

1009
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:48,079
[SPEAKER_02] da mi živimo te svoje riječi,

1010
00:38:48,079 --> 00:38:52,500
[SPEAKER_02] onda mi možemo očekivati da će u njima to zapaliti taj mali plamičak

1011
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:57,179
[SPEAKER_02] koji će oni isto tako pretvoriti u nekakvu svoju komunikaciju.

1012
00:38:58,039 --> 00:39:00,019
[SPEAKER_02] S druge strane, Sveti Augustin je govorio

1013
00:39:00,019 --> 00:39:05,139
[SPEAKER_02] kako ćete zapaliti vatru u drugima ako ne tinja u vama.

1014
00:39:05,139 --> 00:39:09,199
[SPEAKER_02] Moramo vjerovati u to što govorimo, što zastupamo,

1015
00:39:09,199 --> 00:39:10,539
[SPEAKER_02] iza čega stojimo.

1016
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:15,460
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, sve su to važne stvari u komunikaciji o kojima mi ne razmišljamo.

1017
00:39:15,460 --> 00:39:24,380
[SPEAKER_02] Moj rođak, dragi Frajko Skoko, koji je sad trenutačno na putu po Americi,

1018
00:39:24,380 --> 00:39:27,099
[SPEAKER_02] napisao jednu knjigu koja se zove Najveći komunikator.

1019
00:39:27,099 --> 00:39:31,920
[SPEAKER_02] On je doktorirao iz informatskih i komunikatskih znanosti

1020
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:36,760
[SPEAKER_02] na jednoj zanimljivoj temi, komunikacija utemeljitelja velikih religija.

1021
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:40,980
[SPEAKER_02] I on je analizirao kako je komunicirao Isus,

1022
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:44,960
[SPEAKER_02] kako je komunicirao Buda, Muhamed, Konfucije.

1023
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:48,460
[SPEAKER_02] I zapravo je metodološki došao do zaključka

1024
00:39:48,460 --> 00:39:52,440
[SPEAKER_02] kako je Isus bio najveći komunikator koji je hodio po zemlji.

1025
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:56,820
[SPEAKER_02] Njegov mentor je bio pokojni profesor Pavao Novosel,

1026
00:39:56,820 --> 00:40:00,380
[SPEAKER_02] jedan od najvećih komunikologa na prostoru bivše Jugoslavije.

1027
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:01,760
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam imao čas da mi je predavao.

1028
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:07,400
[SPEAKER_02] I sjećam se u jednom društvu je Pavao Novosel rekao

1029
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:12,639
[SPEAKER_02] ma pogledajte samo zgodu Isusa iz Zakeja.

1030
00:40:12,639 --> 00:40:18,420
[SPEAKER_02] Isus dolazi u grad i svi koji se smatraju vjernicima

1031
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:20,760
[SPEAKER_02] žele ga primiti u svoj dom.

1032
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:26,280
[SPEAKER_02] Zakej, jadan, pokriva se ušima,

1033
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:29,739
[SPEAKER_02] on je ipak carinik, dolazi iz jednog ovako miljeja

1034
00:40:29,739 --> 00:40:30,920
[SPEAKER_02] koje nije bilo popularno,

1035
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:32,880
[SPEAKER_02] boji se Isusa pogledati u oči,

1036
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:34,059
[SPEAKER_02] ali je jako znati željan.

1037
00:40:34,059 --> 00:40:35,860
[SPEAKER_02] Isus pristupa njemu i kaže

1038
00:40:35,860 --> 00:40:38,619
[SPEAKER_02] Zakeju, večeras ću boraviti u tvojoj kući.

1039
00:40:39,539 --> 00:40:41,260
[SPEAKER_02] Koja je to poruka Zakeju,

1040
00:40:41,260 --> 00:40:42,699
[SPEAKER_02] kojemu se svijet okreće

1041
00:40:42,699 --> 00:40:46,059
[SPEAKER_02] i koji postaje veliki Isusov komunikator?

1042
00:40:46,059 --> 00:40:48,920
[SPEAKER_02] Koja je to poruka za sve one licemjere

1043
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:51,519
[SPEAKER_02] koji su ljubili Isusov skute

1044
00:40:51,519 --> 00:40:52,760
[SPEAKER_02] a živjeli potpuno drugačije?

1045
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:57,420
[SPEAKER_02] Uzmite bilo koje od slikovitosti u govoru,

1046
00:40:57,420 --> 00:40:58,860
[SPEAKER_02] načinu obraćanja,

1047
00:40:58,860 --> 00:41:00,760
[SPEAKER_02] odašiljanju poruka,

1048
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:03,599
[SPEAKER_02] mjesta na kojima se Isus obraća,

1049
00:41:03,599 --> 00:41:05,239
[SPEAKER_02] zgode koje koristi

1050
00:41:05,239 --> 00:41:08,440
[SPEAKER_02] u današnje doba,

1051
00:41:08,440 --> 00:41:11,679
[SPEAKER_02] nikoga ne je uspio nadmašiti u tome.

1052
00:41:11,679 --> 00:41:13,500
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da mi imamo savršene uzore.

1053
00:41:13,500 --> 00:41:15,639
[SPEAKER_02] Samo je pitanje koliko se mi trudimo

1054
00:41:15,639 --> 00:41:18,119
[SPEAKER_02] i zato ćemo postati dobri komunikatori

1055
00:41:18,119 --> 00:41:21,260
[SPEAKER_02] kada pokušamo izići iz te rutine

1056
00:41:21,260 --> 00:41:23,579
[SPEAKER_02] i počnemo malo analizirati svoju komunikaciju.

1057
00:41:23,579 --> 00:41:24,460
[SPEAKER_02] Kako ja razgovaram?

1058
00:41:24,460 --> 00:41:26,820
[SPEAKER_02] Kako možda onaj koji preko puta

1059
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:28,380
[SPEAKER_02] mene želi da se komunicira s njima?

1060
00:41:28,380 --> 00:41:29,840
[SPEAKER_02] Hoćemo ga povrijediti

1061
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:31,639
[SPEAKER_02] ako mu kažemo baš sve što mislimo?

1062
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:34,719
[SPEAKER_02] Često je znam našaliti pa kažem

1063
00:41:34,719 --> 00:41:37,199
[SPEAKER_02] kolegica vas neka pita

1064
00:41:37,199 --> 00:41:39,300
[SPEAKER_02] kako mi stoji haljina.

1065
00:41:39,300 --> 00:41:41,000
[SPEAKER_02] Sprema se za večernji izlazak.

1066
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:44,360
[SPEAKER_02] Ona je izdvojila cijelu plaću

1067
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:46,159
[SPEAKER_02] da je kupi kod poznatej dizajnerice.

1068
00:41:46,159 --> 00:41:48,320
[SPEAKER_02] Haljina joj iskreno grozno stoji.

1069
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:50,340
[SPEAKER_02] Šta ćete joj reći?

1070
00:41:50,340 --> 00:41:53,239
[SPEAKER_02] Šta ćete joj reći?

1071
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:03,019
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo morate razmisliti

1072
00:42:03,019 --> 00:42:05,460
[SPEAKER_02] ako joj iskreno kažete

1073
00:42:05,460 --> 00:42:07,460
[SPEAKER_02] uništit ćete joj večer.

1074
00:42:07,460 --> 00:42:08,639
[SPEAKER_02] Uništit ćete joj dal.

1075
00:42:08,639 --> 00:42:10,699
[SPEAKER_02] A opet ne možete kontra sebe.

1076
00:42:10,699 --> 00:42:11,780
[SPEAKER_02] Ne možete lagati sebe.

1077
00:42:11,780 --> 00:42:15,159
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, poanta je da se uživite u osobu

1078
00:42:15,159 --> 00:42:17,480
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno njezi način razmišljanja

1079
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:19,000
[SPEAKER_02] i pokušate odaslati poruku

1080
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,559
[SPEAKER_02] a da ne rušite mostove

1081
00:42:20,559 --> 00:42:22,559
[SPEAKER_02] da ne povrijedite čovjeka.

1082
00:42:22,559 --> 00:42:24,900
[SPEAKER_02] Autor Malog princa

1083
00:42:24,900 --> 00:42:26,659
[SPEAKER_02] je rekao

1084
00:42:26,659 --> 00:42:28,699
[SPEAKER_02] nema ništa gore

1085
00:42:28,699 --> 00:42:31,199
[SPEAKER_02] nego da povrijedite čovjeka

1086
00:42:31,199 --> 00:42:32,659
[SPEAKER_02] o njegovim vlastitim očima.

1087
00:42:32,659 --> 00:42:35,019
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, poniziti drugoga.

1088
00:42:35,019 --> 00:42:36,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, nego ga motivirajte.

1089
00:42:36,559 --> 00:42:38,179
[SPEAKER_02] Motivirajte

1090
00:42:38,179 --> 00:42:40,239
[SPEAKER_02] da napravi nešto pozitivno.

1091
00:42:40,239 --> 00:42:42,239
[SPEAKER_02] I zato ponovno se vraćamo

1092
00:42:42,239 --> 00:42:44,440
[SPEAKER_02] ovim političkim debatama

1093
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:49,219
[SPEAKER_02] u kojima ponekad se nađem

1094
00:42:49,219 --> 00:42:50,719
[SPEAKER_02] pa moram zastupati jednu stranu

1095
00:42:50,719 --> 00:42:52,820
[SPEAKER_02] pa imam nekoga preko puta sebe

1096
00:42:52,820 --> 00:42:54,420
[SPEAKER_02] koji zastupa nešto potpuno drugačije.

1097
00:42:54,420 --> 00:42:57,239
[SPEAKER_02] Ono što najveću grešku

1098
00:42:57,239 --> 00:42:58,219
[SPEAKER_02] koju možete napraviti

1099
00:42:58,219 --> 00:42:59,619
[SPEAKER_02] jeste, ne gospodine,

1100
00:42:59,619 --> 00:43:01,219
[SPEAKER_02] ja se uopće ne slažem s vama,

1101
00:43:01,219 --> 00:43:03,239
[SPEAKER_02] to su gluposti o čemu vi govorite,

1102
00:43:03,239 --> 00:43:03,780
[SPEAKER_02] točka.

1103
00:43:03,780 --> 00:43:04,940
[SPEAKER_02] Šta ste vi napravili time?

1104
00:43:04,940 --> 00:43:06,360
[SPEAKER_02] Podigli ste zid

1105
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:08,639
[SPEAKER_02] i zapravo ona njegova publika

1106
00:43:08,639 --> 00:43:11,239
[SPEAKER_02] jednostavno je kontra vas.

1107
00:43:11,539 --> 00:43:12,840
[SPEAKER_02] i vi ste ih zauvijek izgubili.

1108
00:43:12,840 --> 00:43:15,280
[SPEAKER_02] Ali zato ima jedno komunikatsko pravilo

1109
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:15,920
[SPEAKER_02] koje se kaže

1110
00:43:15,920 --> 00:43:17,719
[SPEAKER_02] granja zlatnih mostova.

1111
00:43:17,719 --> 00:43:20,539
[SPEAKER_02] Vi poštujete čovjeka,

1112
00:43:20,539 --> 00:43:21,980
[SPEAKER_02] vi ga i dalje poštujete,

1113
00:43:21,980 --> 00:43:23,519
[SPEAKER_02] ali malo pomalo

1114
00:43:23,519 --> 00:43:25,320
[SPEAKER_02] srušite njegove argumente

1115
00:43:25,320 --> 00:43:26,579
[SPEAKER_02] i njegovu publiku

1116
00:43:26,579 --> 00:43:27,599
[SPEAKER_02] zlatnim mostom

1117
00:43:27,599 --> 00:43:28,960
[SPEAKER_02] prevedete na svoju stranu.

1118
00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:30,260
[SPEAKER_02] Kako to napravite?

1119
00:43:30,260 --> 00:43:31,840
[SPEAKER_02] Pokažete malo poštovanja.

1120
00:43:31,840 --> 00:43:33,019
[SPEAKER_02] Da, gospodine,

1121
00:43:33,019 --> 00:43:34,679
[SPEAKER_02] dijelom se mogu složiti

1122
00:43:34,679 --> 00:43:35,780
[SPEAKER_02] s vašim razmišljanjima,

1123
00:43:35,780 --> 00:43:37,000
[SPEAKER_02] ali morate uzeti obzir

1124
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:37,719
[SPEAKER_02] još dvije stvari.

1125
00:43:37,719 --> 00:43:38,739
[SPEAKER_02] Prva, pazite.

1126
00:43:39,019 --> 00:43:40,820
[SPEAKER_02] i onda rušite, rušite, rušite argumente,

1127
00:43:40,820 --> 00:43:42,039
[SPEAKER_02] vi ste dobili njegovu publiku,

1128
00:43:42,039 --> 00:43:43,179
[SPEAKER_02] njega niste povrijedili,

1129
00:43:43,179 --> 00:43:44,739
[SPEAKER_02] vukcite ovce na broju.

1130
00:43:44,739 --> 00:43:46,840
[SPEAKER_02] To će vam napraviti dobri komunikatori.

1131
00:43:49,320 --> 00:43:50,260
[SPEAKER_03] Sirah, kaže.

1132
00:43:50,260 --> 00:43:52,780
[SPEAKER_03] Mek jezik, lomi kosti.

1133
00:43:52,780 --> 00:43:54,920
[SPEAKER_03] Pa me pocitilo na to pravilo.

1134
00:43:54,920 --> 00:43:56,940
[SPEAKER_03] Evo, spomenuli ste Isusa

1135
00:43:56,940 --> 00:43:58,539
[SPEAKER_03] kao najbolje komunikatora.

1136
00:43:58,539 --> 00:44:00,420
[SPEAKER_03] On kaže, ljubite jedni druge.

1137
00:44:00,420 --> 00:44:02,440
[SPEAKER_03] Htio bi da pređemo možda

1138
00:44:02,440 --> 00:44:03,780
[SPEAKER_03] na novi set pitanja.

1139
00:44:03,780 --> 00:44:06,599
[SPEAKER_03] To je, kako Hrvati ljube bližnje?

1140
00:44:10,099 --> 00:44:11,380
[SPEAKER_03] Određeni smo jednostavno

1141
00:44:11,380 --> 00:44:12,699
[SPEAKER_03] da budemo jedan narod.

1142
00:44:12,699 --> 00:44:14,360
[SPEAKER_03] Bog nas je tu stavio.

1143
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:17,239
[SPEAKER_03] Kako Hrvati gledaju na Hrvatsku?

1144
00:44:17,239 --> 00:44:19,840
[SPEAKER_03] A kako ostali gledaju na Hrvatsku?

1145
00:44:19,840 --> 00:44:22,159
[SPEAKER_03] Vi ste se bavili tim pitanjem.

1146
00:44:23,739 --> 00:44:23,940
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

1147
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:27,219
[SPEAKER_02] Jedan novinar koji je za vrijeme

1148
00:44:27,219 --> 00:44:30,000
[SPEAKER_02] domovinskog rata

1149
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:32,739
[SPEAKER_02] izveštavao s prostora Bivše Jugoslavije,

1150
00:44:32,739 --> 00:44:34,880
[SPEAKER_02] mislim da se prezivao Hejs,

1151
00:44:34,880 --> 00:44:35,760
[SPEAKER_02] ili tako nekako,

1152
00:44:35,760 --> 00:44:37,780
[SPEAKER_02] dobio je Pulicerovu nagradu

1153
00:44:37,780 --> 00:44:40,079
[SPEAKER_02] za izveštavanje s područja Bivše Jugoslavije.

1154
00:44:40,079 --> 00:44:44,880
[SPEAKER_02] Pitali su ga jednom intervjuu,

1155
00:44:44,880 --> 00:44:47,239
[SPEAKER_02] ok, nama ništa nije jasno

1156
00:44:47,239 --> 00:44:49,239
[SPEAKER_02] ko je ko na području Bivše Jugoslavije,

1157
00:44:49,239 --> 00:44:50,340
[SPEAKER_02] dajte nam recite

1158
00:44:50,340 --> 00:44:53,159
[SPEAKER_02] koja je ključna razlika između Srba i Hrvata.

1159
00:44:53,159 --> 00:44:56,039
[SPEAKER_02] I on je dao jednu savršenu diagnozu

1160
00:44:56,039 --> 00:44:57,239
[SPEAKER_02] koju se rado uvijek sjetim.

1161
00:44:57,239 --> 00:44:58,260
[SPEAKER_02] On je rekao

1162
00:44:58,260 --> 00:45:01,900
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati imaju previše kompleksa,

1163
00:45:01,900 --> 00:45:02,960
[SPEAKER_02] a Srbi premalo.

1164
00:45:02,960 --> 00:45:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] I tu se skriva dosta, dosta istine.

1165
00:45:09,800 --> 00:45:13,780
[SPEAKER_01] To je pogled iz valja.

1166
00:45:13,780 --> 00:45:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Hrvati su jedan specifičan narod.

1167
00:45:17,079 --> 00:45:19,400
[SPEAKER_01] Imali smo tešku povijest

1168
00:45:19,400 --> 00:45:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] koja nas je oblikovala,

1169
00:45:20,880 --> 00:45:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] takvi kakvi jesmo.

1170
00:45:22,480 --> 00:45:25,360
[SPEAKER_02] I ako pogledamo,

1171
00:45:25,360 --> 00:45:27,599
[SPEAKER_02] a pisao sam o tome nešto,

1172
00:45:27,599 --> 00:45:28,480
[SPEAKER_02] pisao sam u knjizi

1173
00:45:28,480 --> 00:45:29,360
[SPEAKER_02] Kakvi su Hrvati,

1174
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:31,079
[SPEAKER_02] i tu mi je inspiracija bio jedan

1175
00:45:31,079 --> 00:45:31,920
[SPEAKER_02] moj profesor,

1176
00:45:31,920 --> 00:45:33,500
[SPEAKER_02] sad je pokojni,

1177
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:34,400
[SPEAKER_02] zvao se Edvard Kale.

1178
00:45:34,400 --> 00:45:36,719
[SPEAKER_02] On je napisao jednu sjajanju knjigu

1179
00:45:36,719 --> 00:45:38,099
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvatski kulturni identitet.

1180
00:45:38,099 --> 00:45:40,739
[SPEAKER_02] I on je kroz povijest analizirao

1181
00:45:40,739 --> 00:45:42,199
[SPEAKER_02] kako su se Hrvati ponašali

1182
00:45:42,199 --> 00:45:44,599
[SPEAKER_02] i uspoređivao sa drugim narodima

1183
00:45:44,599 --> 00:45:45,920
[SPEAKER_02] i on je došao do

1184
00:45:45,920 --> 00:45:48,079
[SPEAKER_02] nekoliko zaključaka,

1185
00:45:48,079 --> 00:45:49,300
[SPEAKER_02] a to je da Hrvati imaju

1186
00:45:49,300 --> 00:45:51,400
[SPEAKER_02] istančan osjećaj za pravdu i pravednost.

1187
00:45:51,400 --> 00:45:54,539
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, neki od prvih zakonika

1188
00:45:54,539 --> 00:45:56,000
[SPEAKER_02] su doneseni u Hrvatskoj.

1189
00:45:56,000 --> 00:45:57,159
[SPEAKER_02] Vinodolskog zakonika,

1190
00:45:57,159 --> 00:45:58,400
[SPEAKER_02] pa pogledajmo samo kako su

1191
00:45:58,400 --> 00:45:59,239
[SPEAKER_02] stari Dubrovčani,

1192
00:45:59,239 --> 00:46:00,599
[SPEAKER_02] pa pravaške stranke.

1193
00:46:00,719 --> 00:46:02,239
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, Hrvati vole pravicu.

1194
00:46:02,239 --> 00:46:04,780
[SPEAKER_02] Drugo, Hrvati su se spremni

1195
00:46:04,780 --> 00:46:06,300
[SPEAKER_02] žrtovati za više ideale.

1196
00:46:06,300 --> 00:46:09,079
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, tu ima sada

1197
00:46:09,079 --> 00:46:10,199
[SPEAKER_02] kršćanskog utjecaja,

1198
00:46:10,199 --> 00:46:10,880
[SPEAKER_02] jako,

1199
00:46:10,880 --> 00:46:12,699
[SPEAKER_02] ali ako pogledamo kroz povijest,

1200
00:46:12,699 --> 00:46:13,860
[SPEAKER_02] ako pogledamo velikane,

1201
00:46:13,860 --> 00:46:15,920
[SPEAKER_02] ako pogledamo sve

1202
00:46:15,920 --> 00:46:16,980
[SPEAKER_02] kroz što smo prolazili,

1203
00:46:16,980 --> 00:46:18,360
[SPEAKER_02] onda vidite taj osjećaj.

1204
00:46:18,360 --> 00:46:20,780
[SPEAKER_02] Treće, Hrvati imaju snažan osjećaj

1205
00:46:20,780 --> 00:46:21,519
[SPEAKER_02] prema majici.

1206
00:46:21,519 --> 00:46:23,480
[SPEAKER_02] Majici Božjoj

1207
00:46:23,480 --> 00:46:24,840
[SPEAKER_02] i majici obitelji.

1208
00:46:24,840 --> 00:46:26,579
[SPEAKER_02] Majka Božja, kraljica Hrvata.

1209
00:46:26,579 --> 00:46:28,500
[SPEAKER_02] Uloga majke je obitelji.

1210
00:46:28,500 --> 00:46:31,039
[SPEAKER_02] Tu nas ovom povezuje slično sa Talijanima.

1211
00:46:31,039 --> 00:46:33,280
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

1212
00:46:33,280 --> 00:46:35,340
[SPEAKER_02] i treće,

1213
00:46:35,340 --> 00:46:36,420
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno četvrto,

1214
00:46:36,420 --> 00:46:38,320
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati su jako spremni

1215
00:46:38,320 --> 00:46:40,500
[SPEAKER_02] pomoći jedni drugima

1216
00:46:40,500 --> 00:46:41,780
[SPEAKER_02] u nevolje.

1217
00:46:41,780 --> 00:46:43,500
[SPEAKER_02] I to smo toliko puta vidjeli.

1218
00:46:43,500 --> 00:46:44,079
[SPEAKER_02] Kad je rat,

1219
00:46:44,079 --> 00:46:45,159
[SPEAKER_02] kad je potres,

1220
00:46:45,159 --> 00:46:46,519
[SPEAKER_02] kad je nedača,

1221
00:46:46,519 --> 00:46:48,119
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati će vam dati krvi.

1222
00:46:48,119 --> 00:46:50,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ali čim je mir,

1223
00:46:50,460 --> 00:46:52,219
[SPEAKER_02] onda ćemo se podijeliti.

1224
00:46:52,219 --> 00:46:55,420
[SPEAKER_02] Onda dolazi jedna druga stvar,

1225
00:46:55,420 --> 00:46:56,760
[SPEAKER_02] a to je taj Hrvatski jal.

1226
00:46:57,400 --> 00:46:58,480
[SPEAKER_02] taj Hrvatski jal,

1227
00:46:58,480 --> 00:47:00,000
[SPEAKER_02] kao nešto što je svojstveno nama,

1228
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:01,320
[SPEAKER_02] a to je

1229
00:47:01,320 --> 00:47:02,559
[SPEAKER_02] jedan sociolog,

1230
00:47:02,559 --> 00:47:03,019
[SPEAKER_02] koji se zvao

1231
00:47:03,019 --> 00:47:03,820
[SPEAKER_02] Josip Županov,

1232
00:47:03,820 --> 00:47:04,880
[SPEAKER_02] on je o tome pisao

1233
00:47:04,880 --> 00:47:05,820
[SPEAKER_02] 1991. godine,

1234
00:47:05,820 --> 00:47:06,559
[SPEAKER_02] on je to nazivao

1235
00:47:06,559 --> 00:47:07,699
[SPEAKER_02] egalitarni sindrom.

1236
00:47:07,699 --> 00:47:08,880
[SPEAKER_02] A to je,

1237
00:47:08,880 --> 00:47:09,780
[SPEAKER_02] mi ne volimo

1238
00:47:09,780 --> 00:47:11,460
[SPEAKER_02] da itko strši iznad nas.

1239
00:47:11,460 --> 00:47:14,480
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto je on pametni,

1240
00:47:14,480 --> 00:47:15,980
[SPEAKER_02] zašto on ima bolji auto,

1241
00:47:15,980 --> 00:47:16,860
[SPEAKER_02] zašto...

1242
00:47:16,860 --> 00:47:17,119
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

1243
00:47:17,119 --> 00:47:17,940
[SPEAKER_02] mi ne volimo,

1244
00:47:17,940 --> 00:47:20,159
[SPEAKER_02] volimo kad povučemo dolje

1245
00:47:20,159 --> 00:47:21,159
[SPEAKER_02] i svi smo u blatu,

1246
00:47:21,159 --> 00:47:22,219
[SPEAKER_02] svima nam je teško

1247
00:47:22,219 --> 00:47:22,719
[SPEAKER_02] i to je to.

1248
00:47:22,719 --> 00:47:24,699
[SPEAKER_02] Ne poštujemo tuđi uspjeh

1249
00:47:24,699 --> 00:47:26,800
[SPEAKER_02] i to je recimo nešto što nas koči

1250
00:47:26,800 --> 00:47:27,739
[SPEAKER_02] cijelo vrijeme.

1251
00:47:30,039 --> 00:47:38,300
[SPEAKER_02] I da odgovorim na tvoje ključno pitanje,

1252
00:47:38,300 --> 00:47:41,699
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati o sebi imaju lošije mišljenje

1253
00:47:41,699 --> 00:47:42,900
[SPEAKER_02] nego drugi imaju o nama.

1254
00:47:42,900 --> 00:47:44,719
[SPEAKER_02] Evo,

1255
00:47:44,719 --> 00:47:46,340
[SPEAKER_02] to je jedan zaključak.

1256
00:47:46,340 --> 00:47:46,679
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

1257
00:47:46,679 --> 00:47:48,940
[SPEAKER_02] mi smo jako kritični prema sami sebi

1258
00:47:48,940 --> 00:47:50,599
[SPEAKER_02] i mi,

1259
00:47:50,599 --> 00:47:55,760
[SPEAKER_02] kada bismo imali veće mišljenje o sebi,

1260
00:47:55,760 --> 00:47:58,000
[SPEAKER_02] kao što recimo imaju Amerikanci i Italijani,

1261
00:47:59,099 --> 00:48:00,880
[SPEAKER_02] oni imaju jako razvijenu samosvijest,

1262
00:48:00,880 --> 00:48:01,860
[SPEAKER_02] nacionalni ponos,

1263
00:48:01,860 --> 00:48:03,199
[SPEAKER_02] samo vi to rade simpatično,

1264
00:48:03,199 --> 00:48:04,079
[SPEAKER_02] vi drugi bahato.

1265
00:48:04,079 --> 00:48:06,260
[SPEAKER_02] Mi bi smo bili deleko uspješnije nacija.

1266
00:48:06,260 --> 00:48:06,599
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

1267
00:48:06,599 --> 00:48:09,219
[SPEAKER_02] mi uvijek težimo nekom potvrđivanju iz svijeta.

1268
00:48:09,219 --> 00:48:11,219
[SPEAKER_02] Tek kad iz svijeta pohvale,

1269
00:48:11,219 --> 00:48:11,800
[SPEAKER_02] bravo,

1270
00:48:11,800 --> 00:48:13,019
[SPEAKER_02] onda smo mi sretni.

1271
00:48:13,019 --> 00:48:13,500
[SPEAKER_02] Sve dotada,

1272
00:48:13,500 --> 00:48:13,719
[SPEAKER_02] ne,

1273
00:48:13,719 --> 00:48:14,719
[SPEAKER_02] ništa naše ne valja.

1274
00:48:14,719 --> 00:48:15,920
[SPEAKER_02] Prije,

1275
00:48:15,920 --> 00:48:18,039
[SPEAKER_02] ja mislim tri ili četiri godine,

1276
00:48:18,039 --> 00:48:20,699
[SPEAKER_02] jedna znamstvena istraživačka skupina

1277
00:48:20,699 --> 00:48:21,800
[SPEAKER_02] sa sučilišta Berkeley

1278
00:48:21,800 --> 00:48:24,059
[SPEAKER_02] je radila veliko istraživanje

1279
00:48:24,059 --> 00:48:26,659
[SPEAKER_02] najtolerantnijih naroda na svijetu.

1280
00:48:28,159 --> 00:48:30,199
[SPEAKER_02] između 200 država

1281
00:48:30,199 --> 00:48:31,480
[SPEAKER_02] gdje su oni radili istraživanje,

1282
00:48:31,480 --> 00:48:32,440
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati su,

1283
00:48:32,440 --> 00:48:33,099
[SPEAKER_02] čini mi se,

1284
00:48:33,099 --> 00:48:34,739
[SPEAKER_02] bili na 14. mjesto.

1285
00:48:34,739 --> 00:48:38,099
[SPEAKER_02] Kao najtolerantniji narod

1286
00:48:38,099 --> 00:48:38,980
[SPEAKER_02] u ovom dijelu Evrope.

1287
00:48:40,159 --> 00:48:43,019
[SPEAKER_02] i neki naši novinari su sumnjali u to

1288
00:48:43,019 --> 00:48:44,000
[SPEAKER_02] i pisali su im,

1289
00:48:44,000 --> 00:48:45,179
[SPEAKER_02] vi morate da ste pogriješili,

1290
00:48:45,179 --> 00:48:46,000
[SPEAKER_02] mi smo grozni,

1291
00:48:46,000 --> 00:48:46,840
[SPEAKER_02] mi nismo.

1292
00:48:46,840 --> 00:48:50,099
[SPEAKER_01] Onda jedna članica tima

1293
00:48:50,099 --> 00:48:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] odgovorila jednoj kolegici,

1294
00:48:52,019 --> 00:48:53,239
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam kakvi ste vi,

1295
00:48:53,239 --> 00:48:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] ali drugi su gori od vas.

1296
00:48:54,420 --> 00:48:59,559
[SPEAKER_02] I tek kada dobijemo nekako mjerilo sa drugima,

1297
00:48:59,559 --> 00:49:01,079
[SPEAKER_02] onda mi počnemo vjerovati u sebe.

1298
00:49:01,239 --> 00:49:03,940
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da nama nedostaje samo pouzdanja.

1299
00:49:03,940 --> 00:49:06,619
[SPEAKER_02] Vodimo se idealima,

1300
00:49:06,619 --> 00:49:10,219
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati pokazuju tu jednu dobrotu,

1301
00:49:10,219 --> 00:49:14,679
[SPEAKER_02] ali kada govorimo o usporedbi s drugima,

1302
00:49:14,679 --> 00:49:16,340
[SPEAKER_02] stalno se volimo uspoređivati

1303
00:49:16,340 --> 00:49:20,300
[SPEAKER_02] i nekako imamo taj kompleks manje vrijednosti.

1304
00:49:21,059 --> 00:49:23,239
[SPEAKER_02] Volimo se vraćam na tog velikog komunikologa

1305
00:49:23,239 --> 00:49:24,139
[SPEAKER_02] Pavla Novosela,

1306
00:49:24,139 --> 00:49:26,219
[SPEAKER_02] koji je 1991. godine objavio

1307
00:49:26,219 --> 00:49:28,159
[SPEAKER_02] jedan dobar znanstveni rad,

1308
00:49:28,159 --> 00:49:32,619
[SPEAKER_02] zvao se Hrvatska 1991. i Evropa 1992.

1309
00:49:32,619 --> 00:49:35,199
[SPEAKER_02] I on je napisao tamo

1310
00:49:35,199 --> 00:49:39,260
[SPEAKER_02] da je domovinski rat za Hrvate bio ljekovit.

1311
00:49:39,260 --> 00:49:43,960
[SPEAKER_02] U smislu da smo se mi konačno svočili sa nekim

1312
00:49:43,960 --> 00:49:46,559
[SPEAKER_02] od koga smo se bojali 70 godina

1313
00:49:46,559 --> 00:49:50,380
[SPEAKER_02] i suprostavili se daleko nad moćinjem agresoru

1314
00:49:50,380 --> 00:49:55,900
[SPEAKER_02] i na taj način pokazali zapravo da vjerujemo u sebe.

1315
00:49:55,900 --> 00:49:58,920
[SPEAKER_02] Očekivali smo da će nam Evropa pritiću pomoć,

1316
00:49:58,920 --> 00:50:00,360
[SPEAKER_02] Evropa nas je ostavila na cjedilu

1317
00:50:00,360 --> 00:50:02,719
[SPEAKER_02] i mi smo bez Evrope se izborili za svoju slobodu.

1318
00:50:02,719 --> 00:50:06,579
[SPEAKER_02] I on je smatrao da je to zapravo ključni moment

1319
00:50:06,579 --> 00:50:10,159
[SPEAKER_02] redefiniranja suvremeno hrvatskog nacionalnog identiteta.

1320
00:50:10,159 --> 00:50:11,559
[SPEAKER_02] I to je temelj.

1321
00:50:11,559 --> 00:50:13,800
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim, ta izgradnja novog hrvatskog identiteta

1322
00:50:13,800 --> 00:50:15,599
[SPEAKER_02] se gradila nekje do 1999.

1323
00:50:15,599 --> 00:50:18,920
[SPEAKER_02] I onda se naglo počela urušavati tamo 2000-te

1324
00:50:18,920 --> 00:50:19,699
[SPEAKER_02] sa promjenom vlasti

1325
00:50:19,699 --> 00:50:22,000
[SPEAKER_02] i onda smo dugo, dugo, dugo lutali.

1326
00:50:22,000 --> 00:50:25,000
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da tek sada nekako u kontekstu Evropske unije

1327
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:29,019
[SPEAKER_02] gradimo opet taj neki suvremeni hrvatski nacionalni identitet.

1328
00:50:29,019 --> 00:50:31,880
[SPEAKER_03] Spomenuli ste Evropsku uniju.

1329
00:50:31,880 --> 00:50:33,619
[SPEAKER_03] Naš odnos prema Evropsku uniji,

1330
00:50:33,619 --> 00:50:35,460
[SPEAKER_03] naš kompleks manje vrijednosti,

1331
00:50:35,460 --> 00:50:38,480
[SPEAKER_03] zbog toga i možda nesvjesnosti sami sebe

1332
00:50:38,480 --> 00:50:39,400
[SPEAKER_03] i svog identiteta.

1333
00:50:39,400 --> 00:50:41,079
[SPEAKER_03] Smo možda i slabiji komunikatori

1334
00:50:41,079 --> 00:50:42,219
[SPEAKER_03] nego što bi trebali biti.

1335
00:50:42,219 --> 00:50:45,420
[SPEAKER_03] i možda upravitelj onoga šta imamo.

1336
00:50:45,420 --> 00:50:49,880
[SPEAKER_03] Što možemo dobiti od Evropske unije,

1337
00:50:49,880 --> 00:50:52,119
[SPEAKER_03] a što možda možemo dati Evropske unije?

1338
00:50:54,519 --> 00:50:57,840
[SPEAKER_02] Pa mi po svom i svojim vrijednostima,

1339
00:50:57,840 --> 00:51:01,079
[SPEAKER_02] svome habitusu, svom identitetu pripadamo Evropi.

1340
00:51:01,079 --> 00:51:03,099
[SPEAKER_02] Po meni je bilo logično pitanje

1341
00:51:03,099 --> 00:51:05,719
[SPEAKER_02] da Hrvatska bude sastavna dio Evropske unije.

1342
00:51:05,719 --> 00:51:09,260
[SPEAKER_02] Veliki Marko Marulić, otac Hrvatske književnosti,

1343
00:51:09,260 --> 00:51:10,980
[SPEAKER_02] je pisao dok je

1344
00:51:10,980 --> 00:51:14,039
[SPEAKER_02] najveći dio Evrope bio nepismen,

1345
00:51:14,039 --> 00:51:15,679
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati su objavljivali

1346
00:51:15,679 --> 00:51:17,840
[SPEAKER_02] svoja vrijedna izdanja knjiga.

1347
00:51:17,840 --> 00:51:20,840
[SPEAKER_02] Jer znate da Hrvatska po broju inkunabula

1348
00:51:20,840 --> 00:51:23,039
[SPEAKER_02] je odmah iza Italije.

1349
00:51:23,039 --> 00:51:24,980
[SPEAKER_02] A to se smatra kao

1350
00:51:24,980 --> 00:51:26,840
[SPEAKER_02] svjedočanstvo

1351
00:51:26,840 --> 00:51:29,380
[SPEAKER_02] koliko je bila napredna određena civilizacija

1352
00:51:29,380 --> 00:51:30,300
[SPEAKER_02] u određenom trenutku.

1353
00:51:30,300 --> 00:51:32,820
[SPEAKER_02] Prošli tjedan sam boravio u Irskoj

1354
00:51:32,820 --> 00:51:34,920
[SPEAKER_02] i među ostalim posjetio sam čuvenu

1355
00:51:34,920 --> 00:51:38,039
[SPEAKER_02] knjižnicu na Trinity College u Dublinu.

1356
00:51:38,039 --> 00:51:39,579
[SPEAKER_02] To je ona lijepa knjižnica,

1357
00:51:39,579 --> 00:51:40,880
[SPEAKER_02] jedna od najljepših na svijetu.

1358
00:51:40,880 --> 00:51:43,300
[SPEAKER_02] I sad kreće preuređenje,

1359
00:51:43,300 --> 00:51:45,500
[SPEAKER_02] pa sam imao zadnju priliku ju vidjeti.

1360
00:51:46,059 --> 00:51:48,019
[SPEAKER_02] I u slopu te knjižnice je izložena

1361
00:51:48,019 --> 00:51:51,820
[SPEAKER_02] jedna velika vrijednost te knjižnice.

1362
00:51:51,820 --> 00:51:53,860
[SPEAKER_02] Smatra se najvrijednija knjiga u Irskoj.

1363
00:51:53,860 --> 00:51:56,119
[SPEAKER_02] Zove se Kelska knjiga.

1364
00:51:56,119 --> 00:51:58,019
[SPEAKER_02] Zapravo je jedna vrijedna inkunabula

1365
00:51:58,019 --> 00:51:59,059
[SPEAKER_02] iz osmog stoljeća.

1366
00:51:59,059 --> 00:52:01,559
[SPEAKER_02] I njoj je posvećen dobar dio.

1367
00:52:01,559 --> 00:52:03,619
[SPEAKER_02] I oni oko toga rade savršen PR.

1368
00:52:03,619 --> 00:52:06,500
[SPEAKER_02] I u ogromnoj dvorani je izložena

1369
00:52:06,500 --> 00:52:07,820
[SPEAKER_02] samo jedna knjiga u mraku

1370
00:52:07,820 --> 00:52:09,699
[SPEAKER_02] koju možete vidjeti iz daleka.

1371
00:52:09,699 --> 00:52:11,219
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, oko toga su napravili

1372
00:52:11,219 --> 00:52:12,420
[SPEAKER_02] ogromnu, ogromnu priču.

1373
00:52:13,519 --> 00:52:15,739
[SPEAKER_02] Knjižnica na Trinity koleđu

1374
00:52:15,739 --> 00:52:20,099
[SPEAKER_02] je utemeljena u početkom 17. stoljeća.

1375
00:52:20,099 --> 00:52:21,579
[SPEAKER_02] Na početku imava 30 knjiga,

1376
00:52:21,579 --> 00:52:23,860
[SPEAKER_02] a onda kasnije je izrasla.

1377
00:52:23,860 --> 00:52:25,900
[SPEAKER_02] Stvarno danas ima neke od najvrijednijih knjiga

1378
00:52:25,900 --> 00:52:26,400
[SPEAKER_02] u Irskoj.

1379
00:52:27,579 --> 00:52:30,219
[SPEAKER_02] I sad razgovaram sa nekim našim frvatima

1380
00:52:30,219 --> 00:52:32,760
[SPEAKER_02] joj, blago njima, kako su oni napredna nacija.

1381
00:52:32,760 --> 00:52:33,860
[SPEAKER_02] Vidiš, a di smo mi?

1382
00:52:33,860 --> 00:52:35,840
[SPEAKER_02] Ček, ček, ček, ček, ček.

1383
00:52:35,840 --> 00:52:39,019
[SPEAKER_02] Oni imaju keltsku knjigu iz osmog stoljeća.

1384
00:52:39,019 --> 00:52:42,000
[SPEAKER_02] Mi imamo još ljepši, ljepši,

1385
00:52:42,000 --> 00:52:43,800
[SPEAKER_02] splitski evanđelistar.

1386
00:52:43,800 --> 00:52:46,360
[SPEAKER_02] Iz osmog stoljeća, koji se čuva u Splitskoj katedrali.

1387
00:52:47,000 --> 00:52:49,719
[SPEAKER_02] U to doba, kad su oni osnovali svoju veliku knjižnicu,

1388
00:52:49,719 --> 00:52:52,420
[SPEAKER_02] Isusovci su u Zagrebu pri gimnaziji osnovali

1389
00:52:52,420 --> 00:52:55,820
[SPEAKER_02] svoju knjižnicu koja je imala procedura posudbe knjiga

1390
00:52:55,820 --> 00:52:58,760
[SPEAKER_02] koja je temelj nacionalne sučilišne knjižnice.

1391
00:52:58,760 --> 00:53:01,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ajme, pa nismo znali.

1392
00:53:01,039 --> 00:53:04,820
[SPEAKER_02] I onda sad zafrkavam, kad je Irska u pitanju,

1393
00:53:04,820 --> 00:53:07,239
[SPEAKER_02] pitan svoje studente na petoj godini,

1394
00:53:07,239 --> 00:53:09,000
[SPEAKER_02] bio je blagdan svetog Patrika,

1395
00:53:09,000 --> 00:53:12,739
[SPEAKER_02] jer zna nekog šta je danas, sveti Patrik,

1396
00:53:12,739 --> 00:53:14,719
[SPEAKER_02] šta je on zaštitnik Irske.

1397
00:53:14,719 --> 00:53:16,800
[SPEAKER_02] A koji je zaštitnik Hrvatske?

1398
00:53:17,000 --> 00:53:21,480
[SPEAKER_02] Jedna studentica zna, sveti Josip.

1399
00:53:21,480 --> 00:53:25,880
[SPEAKER_02] I to je problem naš, što mi cijelo vrijeme

1400
00:53:25,880 --> 00:53:27,659
[SPEAKER_02] ono što je naše, a to je bez veze.

1401
00:53:27,659 --> 00:53:29,539
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, ponovo se vraćamo Evropi.

1402
00:53:29,539 --> 00:53:33,539
[SPEAKER_02] Doprinosi koje je Hrvatska dala Evropi su golemi.

1403
00:53:33,539 --> 00:53:36,119
[SPEAKER_02] Ako mi pogledamo samo Hrvatske humaniste,

1404
00:53:36,119 --> 00:53:38,820
[SPEAKER_02] ako pogledamo ponovno se vraća na Marka Marulića,

1405
00:53:38,820 --> 00:53:42,159
[SPEAKER_02] meni draga tema, Marko Marulić u svoje doba

1406
00:53:42,159 --> 00:53:43,880
[SPEAKER_02] je pisao bestsellere u Evropi.

1407
00:53:43,880 --> 00:53:46,940
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, njegove knjige koje su objavljivane

1408
00:53:46,940 --> 00:53:52,519
[SPEAKER_02] na latinskom jeziku su čitali najveća elita toga doba.

1409
00:53:53,519 --> 00:53:57,800
[SPEAKER_02] Profesor Soksforda mi je potvrdio da jedna od najdražih knjiga

1410
00:53:57,800 --> 00:54:00,099
[SPEAKER_02] njihovog velikog kralja Henrika VIII.

1411
00:54:00,099 --> 00:54:05,880
[SPEAKER_02] Bili su Savjeti za dobar život na primjerima Svetaca od Marka Marulića.

1412
00:54:05,880 --> 00:54:08,099
[SPEAKER_02] Navolno je to knjiga koju je držao pod jastukom.

1413
00:54:08,099 --> 00:54:09,440
[SPEAKER_02] Veliki Henrik VIII.

1414
00:54:11,099 --> 00:54:13,219
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto bi onda mi imali komplekse od Evrope?

1415
00:54:13,219 --> 00:54:14,940
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo gradili tu Evropu.

1416
00:54:14,940 --> 00:54:19,440
[SPEAKER_02] Ako pogledamo doprinose hrvatskih latinista, znanstvenika,

1417
00:54:19,440 --> 00:54:21,559
[SPEAKER_02] ostalo, pa mi smo ugrađivali temelje Evropi.

1418
00:54:21,559 --> 00:54:26,380
[SPEAKER_02] Neki od najboljih primjera spomenika evropske renesanse,

1419
00:54:26,380 --> 00:54:27,940
[SPEAKER_02] baroka, nalaze se u Hrvatskoj.

1420
00:54:28,380 --> 00:54:30,320
[SPEAKER_02] Ali mi to nismo posvijestili sebi.

1421
00:54:30,320 --> 00:54:33,679
[SPEAKER_02] I zato mi uvijek gledamo u Evropu kao nekog velikog spasitelja.

1422
00:54:33,679 --> 00:54:38,139
[SPEAKER_02] Recimo, pitanje šta mi možemo podučiti Evropu?

1423
00:54:38,139 --> 00:54:43,480
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znam da li znate, ali Islamska zajednica u Zagrebu

1424
00:54:43,480 --> 00:54:46,519
[SPEAKER_02] je organizirala jedno gostovanje.

1425
00:54:46,519 --> 00:54:48,000
[SPEAKER_02] Čini mi se da je to bilo u Brselu.

1426
00:54:48,000 --> 00:54:52,440
[SPEAKER_02] I bilo se raspravljao oko integracije Islama u Evropi.

1427
00:54:52,440 --> 00:54:56,219
[SPEAKER_02] I onda je predstavnik Islamske zajednice u Zagrebu rekao

1428
00:54:56,219 --> 00:54:57,880
[SPEAKER_02] pa učite od Hrvatske.

1429
00:54:58,380 --> 00:55:02,860
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvatska ima najbolje riješeno pitanje Islama u Evropi.

1430
00:55:02,860 --> 00:55:06,860
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, Hrvatska je kao službenu religiju

1431
00:55:06,860 --> 00:55:09,119
[SPEAKER_02] priznala Islam prije 110 godina.

1432
00:55:09,119 --> 00:55:10,900
[SPEAKER_02] I riješila sve.

1433
00:55:10,900 --> 00:55:14,179
[SPEAKER_02] A danas razvijena Švicarska

1434
00:55:14,179 --> 00:55:17,099
[SPEAKER_02] ne da na referendumu izgraditi minarete.

1435
00:55:17,099 --> 00:55:19,440
[SPEAKER_02] A oni su u jako demokratsko društvo.

1436
00:55:19,440 --> 00:55:23,900
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, stvar je da mi tekako smo u nekim stvarima

1437
00:55:23,900 --> 00:55:28,360
[SPEAKER_02] i tekako napredni možemo podučavati Evropu.

1438
00:55:28,380 --> 00:55:31,679
[SPEAKER_02] samo nemamo toga garda da mi pokažemo

1439
00:55:31,679 --> 00:55:33,340
[SPEAKER_02] da, u nekim stvarima smo unijeliko bolji,

1440
00:55:33,340 --> 00:55:35,019
[SPEAKER_02] otvoreniji, spremniji na dialog.

1441
00:55:35,019 --> 00:55:37,000
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da to je samo jedan od primjera

1442
00:55:37,000 --> 00:55:38,980
[SPEAKER_02] gdje smo mi davno bili Evropa.

1443
00:55:40,860 --> 00:55:45,659
[SPEAKER_03] Evo, po pitanju Hrvatskog identiteta, često se priča da je on neodvojivo od katoličke vjere.

1444
00:55:45,920 --> 00:55:54,199
[SPEAKER_03] Zanima me vaše mišljenje o tome, a s druge strane, evo neka istraživanja pokazuju da smo mi jedna od najnesretnih nacija u Europi.

1445
00:55:54,199 --> 00:55:58,800
[SPEAKER_03] A u isto vrijeme smo, utemeljenje imamo na katoličkoj vjeri.

1446
00:55:58,800 --> 00:56:01,659
[SPEAKER_03] Evo, zanima me vaš pogled na tu situaciju.

1447
00:56:02,719 --> 00:56:09,179
[SPEAKER_03] Ne bi li katolici, krešćani, trajali biti puni nade, optimizma, radosti, kreativnosti?

1448
00:56:09,179 --> 00:56:10,400
[SPEAKER_02] Slažem se.

1449
00:56:10,400 --> 00:56:15,679
[SPEAKER_02] Katoličko u hrvatskom identitetu i katoličko u evropskom identitetu.

1450
00:56:15,679 --> 00:56:16,820
[SPEAKER_02] Ja to ne bi razdvajao.

1451
00:56:16,820 --> 00:56:23,019
[SPEAKER_02] Neki su jako pesimistični, pa onda kažu, evo, Evropa se odrekla krešćanstva.

1452
00:56:23,019 --> 00:56:25,039
[SPEAKER_02] I to je odšlo u nepovrat.

1453
00:56:25,380 --> 00:56:27,179
[SPEAKER_02] Je, na načinoj razini, da.

1454
00:56:27,179 --> 00:56:33,340
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim, ja bi tu više bio skloniji onom razmišljanju Daglasa Mareja,

1455
00:56:33,340 --> 00:56:35,820
[SPEAKER_02] koji je napisao u sjajnu knjigu Čudna smrte Evrope.

1456
00:56:35,820 --> 00:56:38,599
[SPEAKER_02] On je napisao tamo jedan sjajan citat koji kaže

1457
00:56:38,599 --> 00:56:41,079
[SPEAKER_02] Vi možete biti ateist u Evropi,

1458
00:56:41,079 --> 00:56:46,039
[SPEAKER_02] ali ne možete negirati vaš kršćanski identitet.

1459
00:56:46,039 --> 00:56:46,599
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto?

1460
00:56:46,599 --> 00:56:52,400
[SPEAKER_02] Sato što je to kršćanstvo ugrađeno u palače, u katedrale, u glazbu, u umjetnost,

1461
00:56:52,400 --> 00:56:53,760
[SPEAKER_02] u sve ono što te okružuje.

1462
00:56:54,139 --> 00:56:56,800
[SPEAKER_02] I ti možeš glumiti da te kršćanstvo ne zanima onoj tu.

1463
00:56:56,800 --> 00:57:01,019
[SPEAKER_02] By the way, sam autor je ateist koji to lijepo piše.

1464
00:57:01,019 --> 00:57:04,800
[SPEAKER_02] Prema tome, ne može Evropa pobjeći od svojih kršćanskih korijena,

1465
00:57:04,800 --> 00:57:08,760
[SPEAKER_02] jer da nije bilo kršćanstva ne bi bilo tok tih svih blagodati

1466
00:57:08,760 --> 00:57:10,239
[SPEAKER_02] kojima smo danas okruženi.

1467
00:57:10,239 --> 00:57:12,099
[SPEAKER_02] To isto možemo primijeniti i na Hrvatsku.

1468
00:57:12,099 --> 00:57:16,619
[SPEAKER_02] Prema tome, ja bih rekao da je kršćanstvo u nekakvom kodnom zapisu

1469
00:57:16,619 --> 00:57:18,360
[SPEAKER_02] našeg suvremenog identiteta.

1470
00:57:19,300 --> 00:57:26,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ono prožima od kulture, pravnog sustava, načina života i ostalo.

1471
00:57:26,420 --> 00:57:31,199
[SPEAKER_02] Na načinoj razini Evropa nastoji negirati taj svoj identitet

1472
00:57:31,199 --> 00:57:33,679
[SPEAKER_02] tako što će to, Bože, otvoriti se drugima.

1473
00:57:33,679 --> 00:57:37,159
[SPEAKER_02] I onda zapravo radi na štetu kršćanstva

1474
00:57:37,159 --> 00:57:40,619
[SPEAKER_02] političku korektnost prema drugim religijama.

1475
00:57:40,619 --> 00:57:43,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ili, recimo, ne znam ako ste pokušali umjetnoj inteligenciji,

1476
00:57:43,960 --> 00:57:47,940
[SPEAKER_02] sada se svi igraju u njome, pa onda ukucajte,

1477
00:57:47,940 --> 00:57:50,519
[SPEAKER_02] jer možete ispričati jedan vic o islamu.

1478
00:57:50,519 --> 00:57:53,280
[SPEAKER_02] Onda vam umjetna inteligencija odgovori,

1479
00:57:53,280 --> 00:58:00,059
[SPEAKER_02] nije politički uputno i korektno pričati bilo što negativno o islamu.

1480
00:58:00,780 --> 00:58:03,380
[SPEAKER_02] Ispričajte nam jedan vic o kršćanstvu, o, to može.

1481
00:58:03,380 --> 00:58:10,440
[SPEAKER_02] E sad, kreatori umjetne inteligencije znaju zašto su to tako napravili.

1482
00:58:10,440 --> 00:58:13,280
[SPEAKER_02] Ali upravo ta jedna kršćanska otvorenost,

1483
00:58:13,280 --> 00:58:15,980
[SPEAKER_02] da mi okrećemo i drugi obraz, ma pljujte, nema problema,

1484
00:58:15,980 --> 00:58:18,480
[SPEAKER_02] koja druga religija će to napraviti?

1485
00:58:18,480 --> 00:58:20,900
[SPEAKER_02] I to je naš evropski identitet.

1486
00:58:20,900 --> 00:58:24,039
[SPEAKER_02] Prema tome, ja bih rekao da mi ne možemo pobjeći

1487
00:58:24,039 --> 00:58:27,179
[SPEAKER_02] od kršćanskog identiteta zvali se kršćanima ili se ne zvali.

1488
00:58:27,179 --> 00:58:28,300
[SPEAKER_02] On nas prati.

1489
00:58:30,000 --> 00:58:32,880
[SPEAKER_03] Prostore, imamo jedan zanimljiv fenomen,

1490
00:58:32,880 --> 00:58:37,980
[SPEAKER_03] a to je da jedna osoba je možda najveći promotor

1491
00:58:37,980 --> 00:58:42,039
[SPEAKER_03] hrvatskog identiteta više od 40 godina tamo iz vaših krajeva.

1492
00:58:42,039 --> 00:58:43,280
[SPEAKER_03] To je Gospa Međugorska.

1493
00:58:43,280 --> 00:58:46,159
[SPEAKER_03] Priča hrvatski već više od 40 godina.

1494
00:58:46,159 --> 00:58:48,699
[SPEAKER_03] Zanima me, ovo je moje zadnje pitanje.

1495
00:58:48,699 --> 00:58:51,880
[SPEAKER_03] Onda ću dat priliku da postavite sve pitanja.

1496
00:58:51,880 --> 00:58:55,880
[SPEAKER_03] Kako je ovo, vi gledate na taj fenomen?

1497
00:58:57,320 --> 00:59:00,860
[SPEAKER_02] Pa ako gledamo po plodovima, a mislim da bismo to trebali gledati,

1498
00:59:00,860 --> 00:59:03,320
[SPEAKER_02] onda je Međugorje veliki dar.

1499
00:59:03,320 --> 00:59:04,940
[SPEAKER_02] Međugorje veliki dar.

1500
00:59:04,940 --> 00:59:08,960
[SPEAKER_02] Sad, sad, pada mi na pamet, prije 4-5 godina,

1501
00:59:08,960 --> 00:59:12,559
[SPEAKER_02] sam imao raspravu sa jednim svojim kolegom koji je sa mnom studirao,

1502
00:59:13,059 --> 00:59:16,920
[SPEAKER_02] inače ateist, i mi smo razgovarali, on mene pita,

1503
00:59:16,920 --> 00:59:20,539
[SPEAKER_02] ajde mi kaži tri argumenta zašto ti smatraš da se Gospa ukazala.

1504
00:59:20,539 --> 00:59:24,019
[SPEAKER_02] Ja kažem, pa ljudi dolaze i odlaze bolji iz Međugorja.

1505
00:59:24,019 --> 00:59:26,400
[SPEAKER_02] A dobro, to može biti autosugestija.

1506
00:59:26,400 --> 00:59:28,079
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro.

1507
00:59:28,079 --> 00:59:32,559
[SPEAKER_02] Sad ja kažem, dobro, ali imate šestero djece

1508
00:59:32,559 --> 00:59:35,920
[SPEAKER_02] koji ni po čemu ne nadilaze prosjek.

1509
00:59:35,920 --> 00:59:37,619
[SPEAKER_02] To su obični ljudi.

1510
00:59:37,619 --> 00:59:41,099
[SPEAKER_02] I oni 40 godina ponavljaju jedno te isto.

1511
00:59:41,099 --> 00:59:42,860
[SPEAKER_02] Komunisti su ih maltretirali.

1512
00:59:42,860 --> 00:59:45,599
[SPEAKER_02] Svi mogući istraživači iz cijelog svijeta

1513
00:59:45,599 --> 00:59:47,139
[SPEAKER_02] pokušavali su nametiti nešto drugo.

1514
00:59:47,139 --> 00:59:48,860
[SPEAKER_02] Oni uporno ponavljaju jedno te isto.

1515
00:59:48,860 --> 00:59:51,300
[SPEAKER_02] Ok, ajde, dobro.

1516
00:59:51,300 --> 00:59:53,539
[SPEAKER_02] I sad završimo mi razgovor.

1517
00:59:53,539 --> 00:59:55,960
[SPEAKER_02] I on mene zove nakon par dana i kaže

1518
00:59:55,960 --> 00:59:57,659
[SPEAKER_02] ma ne, ne, znaš šta sam razmišljao?

1519
00:59:57,659 --> 01:00:00,019
[SPEAKER_02] A šta ako se stvarno Gospa tamo ukazala?

1520
01:00:00,019 --> 01:00:02,800
[SPEAKER_02] Je li? Ok, šta ako?

1521
01:00:02,800 --> 01:00:04,619
[SPEAKER_02] Pa to bi bila senzacija.

1522
01:00:04,619 --> 01:00:06,400
[SPEAKER_02] Pa to bi bila senzacija.

1523
01:00:06,400 --> 01:00:07,699
[SPEAKER_02] Pa već je senzacija.

1524
01:00:07,699 --> 01:00:09,699
[SPEAKER_02] Ali onda mi je postao jedno pitanje

1525
01:00:09,699 --> 01:00:10,780
[SPEAKER_02] gdje sam seba zamislio.

1526
01:00:10,780 --> 01:00:14,219
[SPEAKER_02] Pa zašto vi kršćani niste sretni zbog toga?

1527
01:00:14,219 --> 01:00:17,179
[SPEAKER_02] Ako postoji vjerojatnost da se Gospa tamo ukazala

1528
01:00:17,179 --> 01:00:18,519
[SPEAKER_02] i progovorila na hrvatskom

1529
01:00:18,519 --> 01:00:21,000
[SPEAKER_02] pa vi bi trebali hodati po svijetu

1530
01:00:21,000 --> 01:00:21,860
[SPEAKER_02] i to sve dočiti.

1531
01:00:21,860 --> 01:00:24,320
[SPEAKER_02] I onda sam, gledaj, imaš pravo.

1532
01:00:24,320 --> 01:00:26,699
[SPEAKER_02] Mi kao da nismo svjesni toga.

1533
01:00:26,699 --> 01:00:28,719
[SPEAKER_02] Govorim sada o svojim hercegovacima,

1534
01:00:28,719 --> 01:00:30,039
[SPEAKER_02] o hrvatima, svi ostali.

1535
01:00:30,039 --> 01:00:31,619
[SPEAKER_02] Nekako to se podrazumijeva.

1536
01:00:31,619 --> 01:00:33,880
[SPEAKER_02] Mi imamo tu milost i to nam je lijepo

1537
01:00:33,880 --> 01:00:35,480
[SPEAKER_02] i dolazi nam cijeli svijet

1538
01:00:35,480 --> 01:00:36,820
[SPEAKER_02] i mi slušamo poruke,

1539
01:00:36,820 --> 01:00:39,880
[SPEAKER_02] ali premalo mijenjamo svoje živote

1540
01:00:39,880 --> 01:00:41,000
[SPEAKER_02] sa ukladnom tim porukama.

1541
01:00:41,000 --> 01:00:43,800
[SPEAKER_02] I mislim da se tu nalazi

1542
01:00:43,800 --> 01:00:44,719
[SPEAKER_02] jedan blagi raskorak.

1543
01:00:44,719 --> 01:00:45,880
[SPEAKER_02] Da bi smo mi trebali biti,

1544
01:00:45,880 --> 01:00:48,099
[SPEAKER_02] koji živimo u to milosno vrijeme

1545
01:00:48,099 --> 01:00:50,280
[SPEAKER_02] i koji možemo biti dio

1546
01:00:50,280 --> 01:00:51,679
[SPEAKER_02] tog čuda,

1547
01:00:52,519 --> 01:00:54,000
[SPEAKER_02] da mi to ne prenesemo

1548
01:00:54,000 --> 01:00:55,079
[SPEAKER_02] na druge svojim životom.

1549
01:00:55,079 --> 01:00:57,460
[SPEAKER_02] To mi nekako nedostaje.

1550
01:00:57,460 --> 01:01:00,019
[SPEAKER_02] A naravno,

1551
01:01:00,019 --> 01:01:02,260
[SPEAKER_02] ljudski je vjerovati ili ne vjerovati.

1552
01:01:02,260 --> 01:01:02,980
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim,

1553
01:01:02,980 --> 01:01:04,960
[SPEAKER_02] Toma je sumljao.

1554
01:01:04,960 --> 01:01:08,420
[SPEAKER_02] Pojedini ljudi iz crkve

1555
01:01:08,420 --> 01:01:09,300
[SPEAKER_02] imaju pravo sumljati,

1556
01:01:09,300 --> 01:01:10,840
[SPEAKER_02] jer to mogu biti

1557
01:01:10,840 --> 01:01:13,059
[SPEAKER_02] koje ne iziskuju

1558
01:01:13,059 --> 01:01:16,539
[SPEAKER_02] nekakav jasan stav.

1559
01:01:16,880 --> 01:01:18,920
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ako se gospoda ukazala

1560
01:01:18,920 --> 01:01:20,000
[SPEAKER_02] u Fatim i u Lurdu,

1561
01:01:20,000 --> 01:01:21,340
[SPEAKER_02] zašto ne bi nastavila tamo

1562
01:01:21,340 --> 01:01:22,340
[SPEAKER_02] gdje je stala u Međugorju?

1563
01:01:22,340 --> 01:01:23,300
[SPEAKER_02] Pogotovo,

1564
01:01:23,300 --> 01:01:24,079
[SPEAKER_02] zašto Međugorje?

1565
01:01:24,079 --> 01:01:25,699
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto Međugorje?

1566
01:01:25,699 --> 01:01:29,420
[SPEAKER_02] Zamolio me jedan časopis

1567
01:01:29,420 --> 01:01:30,400
[SPEAKER_02] da napišem jedan rad

1568
01:01:30,400 --> 01:01:31,539
[SPEAKER_02] o tome

1569
01:01:31,539 --> 01:01:32,780
[SPEAKER_02] zašto Međugorje?

1570
01:01:32,780 --> 01:01:36,960
[SPEAKER_02] I dugo sam okljevao

1571
01:01:36,960 --> 01:01:38,400
[SPEAKER_02] oko toga šta ću pisati sada,

1572
01:01:38,400 --> 01:01:39,139
[SPEAKER_02] jer svi ono pišu

1573
01:01:39,139 --> 01:01:40,739
[SPEAKER_02] a dolje je tradicionalna vjera,

1574
01:01:40,739 --> 01:01:41,880
[SPEAKER_02] ok, dobro,

1575
01:01:41,880 --> 01:01:42,519
[SPEAKER_02] pa ne znam,

1576
01:01:42,519 --> 01:01:43,940
[SPEAKER_02] ono doba, pa o, pa ono.

1577
01:01:43,940 --> 01:01:45,900
[SPEAKER_02] I dugo sam ja odgađao

1578
01:01:45,900 --> 01:01:47,079
[SPEAKER_02] taj članak

1579
01:01:47,079 --> 01:01:49,239
[SPEAKER_02] i sada Dug Sveti djeluje,

1580
01:01:49,239 --> 01:01:51,619
[SPEAKER_02] ja slučajno među starim papirima,

1581
01:01:51,619 --> 01:01:52,940
[SPEAKER_02] starim papirima,

1582
01:01:52,940 --> 01:01:55,139
[SPEAKER_02] nalazim čuveni rad

1583
01:01:55,139 --> 01:01:57,000
[SPEAKER_02] od Samuela Huntingtona

1584
01:01:57,000 --> 01:01:58,980
[SPEAKER_02] koji se bavio sukobom civilizacija.

1585
01:01:58,980 --> 01:02:01,019
[SPEAKER_02] I čitam taj rad

1586
01:02:01,019 --> 01:02:02,179
[SPEAKER_02] i on kaže

1587
01:02:02,179 --> 01:02:05,800
[SPEAKER_02] postoje šest žarišta u svijetu,

1588
01:02:05,800 --> 01:02:07,739
[SPEAKER_02] dakle on je to pisao negdje

1589
01:02:07,739 --> 01:02:09,360
[SPEAKER_02] još kasnih 80. godina,

1590
01:02:09,360 --> 01:02:11,400
[SPEAKER_02] šest žarišta u svijetu

1591
01:02:11,400 --> 01:02:13,139
[SPEAKER_02] gdje se dodiruju

1592
01:02:13,139 --> 01:02:15,880
[SPEAKER_02] i sudaraju veliki civilizacijski,

1593
01:02:15,880 --> 01:02:17,239
[SPEAKER_02] religijski krugovi.

1594
01:02:17,239 --> 01:02:18,679
[SPEAKER_02] I onda je nabraja,

1595
01:02:18,679 --> 01:02:20,059
[SPEAKER_02] pam, pam, pam, pam,

1596
01:02:20,059 --> 01:02:21,500
[SPEAKER_02] Bosna i Hercegovina.

1597
01:02:21,500 --> 01:02:25,059
[SPEAKER_02] Kaže, tamo se susreću svijetovi.

1598
01:02:25,059 --> 01:02:27,420
[SPEAKER_02] Tamo može biti razdjelnica,

1599
01:02:27,420 --> 01:02:28,699
[SPEAKER_02] može biti susretište.

1600
01:02:28,699 --> 01:02:29,460
[SPEAKER_02] I onda sam napisao,

1601
01:02:29,460 --> 01:02:30,139
[SPEAKER_02] temeljem toga,

1602
01:02:30,139 --> 01:02:30,860
[SPEAKER_02] upravo to,

1603
01:02:30,860 --> 01:02:33,139
[SPEAKER_02] zašto Bosna i Hercegovina.

1604
01:02:33,139 --> 01:02:35,519
[SPEAKER_02] Zato što se tamo

1605
01:02:35,519 --> 01:02:36,860
[SPEAKER_02] dijele svijetovi,

1606
01:02:36,860 --> 01:02:38,820
[SPEAKER_02] istok, zapad,

1607
01:02:38,820 --> 01:02:41,599
[SPEAKER_02] ali može biti i susretište.

1608
01:02:41,599 --> 01:02:43,820
[SPEAKER_02] I upravo Međugorje postaje susretište.

1609
01:02:43,820 --> 01:02:45,280
[SPEAKER_02] Postaje susretište

1610
01:02:45,280 --> 01:02:46,960
[SPEAKER_02] koje nastoji mijenjati taj svijet.

1611
01:02:46,960 --> 01:02:48,679
[SPEAKER_02] Uzmimo samo da

1612
01:02:48,679 --> 01:02:49,780
[SPEAKER_02] deset godina nakon

1613
01:02:49,780 --> 01:02:50,940
[SPEAKER_02] međugorskih ukazanja

1614
01:02:50,940 --> 01:02:52,119
[SPEAKER_02] je upravo na tom području

1615
01:02:52,119 --> 01:02:53,579
[SPEAKER_02] koje opisivao i Huntington

1616
01:02:53,579 --> 01:02:55,320
[SPEAKER_02] dogodio se najkrvavi rat

1617
01:02:55,320 --> 01:02:56,280
[SPEAKER_02] na koji mi smo mogli

1618
01:02:56,280 --> 01:02:56,960
[SPEAKER_02] ni zamišljati.

1619
01:02:56,960 --> 01:02:58,480
[SPEAKER_02] Ali

1620
01:02:58,480 --> 01:03:01,059
[SPEAKER_02] Međugorje što je uvijek

1621
01:03:01,059 --> 01:03:01,920
[SPEAKER_02] jedna velika tajna

1622
01:03:01,920 --> 01:03:02,739
[SPEAKER_02] koju svakodnevno

1623
01:03:02,739 --> 01:03:03,679
[SPEAKER_02] moramo otkrivati,

1624
01:03:03,679 --> 01:03:04,980
[SPEAKER_02] iščekivati,

1625
01:03:04,980 --> 01:03:07,360
[SPEAKER_02] ali ono što mene sad golica,

1626
01:03:07,360 --> 01:03:07,860
[SPEAKER_02] to mi je sad

1627
01:03:07,860 --> 01:03:09,099
[SPEAKER_02] novinarska znatiželja.

1628
01:03:09,099 --> 01:03:11,460
[SPEAKER_02] To mi je novinarska znatiželja.

1629
01:03:11,460 --> 01:03:13,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ako je Gospa

1630
01:03:13,039 --> 01:03:13,880
[SPEAKER_02] dala

1631
01:03:13,880 --> 01:03:15,500
[SPEAKER_02] deset tajni,

1632
01:03:15,500 --> 01:03:19,159
[SPEAKER_02] ako će se otkriti

1633
01:03:19,159 --> 01:03:19,800
[SPEAKER_02] neke tajne

1634
01:03:19,800 --> 01:03:20,679
[SPEAKER_02] u dogledno vrijeme,

1635
01:03:20,679 --> 01:03:22,940
[SPEAKER_02] ako bi te tajne trebao

1636
01:03:22,940 --> 01:03:24,920
[SPEAKER_02] predošiti svijetu

1637
01:03:24,920 --> 01:03:26,219
[SPEAKER_02] svećenik koji je u tom trenutku

1638
01:03:26,219 --> 01:03:27,039
[SPEAKER_02] bio u Međugorju,

1639
01:03:27,039 --> 01:03:28,320
[SPEAKER_02] fra Petar,

1640
01:03:28,320 --> 01:03:30,179
[SPEAKER_02] a on je već u podmakloj dobi

1641
01:03:30,179 --> 01:03:33,260
[SPEAKER_02] živimo li u posljednjim vremenima.

1642
01:03:33,260 --> 01:03:35,599
[SPEAKER_02] To je sad novinarski,

1643
01:03:35,599 --> 01:03:37,320
[SPEAKER_02] to nije...

1644
01:03:37,320 --> 01:03:37,679
[SPEAKER_02] Ali

1645
01:03:37,679 --> 01:03:39,599
[SPEAKER_02] puno to otvara pitanja,

1646
01:03:39,599 --> 01:03:40,519
[SPEAKER_02] ali mislim da je Međugorje

1647
01:03:40,519 --> 01:03:41,199
[SPEAKER_02] velika milost

1648
01:03:41,199 --> 01:03:41,900
[SPEAKER_02] koju bi smo trebali

1649
01:03:41,900 --> 01:03:43,300
[SPEAKER_02] prihvatiti i širiti svijetom.

1650
01:03:43,300 --> 01:03:44,360
[SPEAKER_03] Profesor,

1651
01:03:44,360 --> 01:03:45,900
[SPEAKER_03] responjali ste Bosnu i Hercegunu.

1652
01:03:45,900 --> 01:03:47,699
[SPEAKER_03] Dok se ljudi pripreme za pitanja,

1653
01:03:47,699 --> 01:03:49,260
[SPEAKER_03] Matija ima pitanje.

1654
01:03:54,519 --> 01:03:57,139
[SPEAKER_04] Neće biti o Bosni i Hercegovini,

1655
01:03:57,139 --> 01:03:58,420
[SPEAKER_04] tu mi je sve jasno.

1656
01:03:58,420 --> 01:04:02,860
[SPEAKER_04] Tu su se složili

1657
01:04:02,860 --> 01:04:05,039
[SPEAKER_04] i katolički,

1658
01:04:05,039 --> 01:04:06,559
[SPEAKER_04] i pravoslavni,

1659
01:04:06,559 --> 01:04:07,820
[SPEAKER_04] i muslimanski teolozi

1660
01:04:07,820 --> 01:04:09,719
[SPEAKER_04] da je Bosnu nemoguće razumijet,

1661
01:04:09,719 --> 01:04:10,539
[SPEAKER_04] kao ni žene,

1662
01:04:10,539 --> 01:04:11,679
[SPEAKER_04] ali ako se zavoli,

1663
01:04:11,679 --> 01:04:12,960
[SPEAKER_04] onda će se razumijet.

1664
01:04:12,960 --> 01:04:14,059
[SPEAKER_04] Ali,

1665
01:04:14,059 --> 01:04:16,639
[SPEAKER_04] jedno pitanje možda vezano

1666
