1667
01:04:18,579 --> 01:04:20,039
[SPEAKER_04] Vidili smo da je tu bilo

1668
01:04:20,039 --> 01:04:21,539
[SPEAKER_04] i uloge medija,

1669
01:04:21,539 --> 01:04:23,639
[SPEAKER_04] pa bih tio možda vaš osvrt,

1670
01:04:23,639 --> 01:04:25,480
[SPEAKER_04] ključna uloga medija,

1671
01:04:25,480 --> 01:04:26,619
[SPEAKER_04] vaš osvrt,

1672
01:04:26,619 --> 01:04:29,260
