[SPEAKER_04] prema javnosti

1676
01:04:33,480 --> 01:04:34,500
[SPEAKER_04] u toj krizi

1677
01:04:34,500 --> 01:04:35,639
[SPEAKER_04] koja je stvarno potresla.

1678
01:04:35,639 --> 01:04:37,000
[SPEAKER_04] Sve kod nas je bila pojačana

1679
01:04:37,000 --> 01:04:37,960
[SPEAKER_04] i tim potresima

1680
