[SPEAKER_04] bilo političkih,

1684
01:04:43,760 --> 01:04:44,440
[SPEAKER_04] bilo vjerskih,

1685
01:04:44,440 --> 01:04:45,579
[SPEAKER_04] istaknuli kao primjer

1686
01:04:45,579 --> 01:04:47,260
[SPEAKER_04] najboljeg komunikatora

1687
01:04:47,260 --> 01:04:49,420
[SPEAKER_04] u toj kriznoj situaciji.

1688
01:04:49,420 --> 01:04:51,840
[SPEAKER_04] Neobisno sad

1689
01:04:51,840 --> 01:04:52,519
[SPEAKER_04] koja je strana,

1690
01:04:52,519 --> 01:04:53,340
[SPEAKER_04] za cijepljenje,

1691
01:04:53,340 --> 01:04:54,000
[SPEAKER_04] ne maske,

1692
01:04:54,000 --> 01:04:54,699
[SPEAKER_04] ne maske,

1693
01:04:54,699 --> 01:04:56,159
[SPEAKER_04] bilo je puno tabora,

1694
01:04:56,159 --> 01:04:56,920
[SPEAKER_04] ali evo,

1695
