[SPEAKER_02] vrlo malo,

1708
01:05:15,880 --> 01:05:18,980
[SPEAKER_02] ali ako općenito gledamo

1709
01:05:18,980 --> 01:05:20,860
[SPEAKER_02] snalaženje čak i duhovnih pastira,

1710
